  ANIMALS OF THE WORLD
============================================================

Name:         Arctic Fox
Scientific:   Vulpes lagopus
Class:        Mammalia
Habitat:      Arctic tundra
Diet:         Omnivore
Lifespan:     3 years
Weight:       3.5 kg
Status:       Least Concern
Fact:         Fur changes color seasonally; survives -70 degrees Celsius

Name:         Giant Panda
Scientific:   Ailuropoda melanoleuca
Class:        Mammalia
Habitat:      Temperate forest
Diet:         Herbivore
Lifespan:     20 years
Weight:       100 kg
Status:       Vulnerable
Fact:         Eats 12-38 kg bamboo daily; has a sixth finger (pseudo-thumb)

Name:         Blue Whale
Scientific:   Balaenoptera musculus
Class:        Mammalia
Habitat:      Ocean
Diet:         Carnivore (krill)
Lifespan:     80 years
Weight:       150000 kg
Status:       Endangered
Fact:         Largest animal ever known; heart is size of a small car

